<h1><%= @energy_application %></h1>

<p>Submission Date: <%= @energy_application.submission_date %></p>

<h2>Basic Information</h2>
<p>First Name: <%= @energy_application.first_name %></p>
<p>Last Name: <%= @energy_application.last_name %></p>
<p>Phone Number: <%= @energy_application.phone_number %></p>
<p>Phone Type: <%= @energy_application.phone_type %></p>
<p>Email Address: <%= @energy_application.email_address %></p>
<p>How Necessities Are Paid <%= @energy_application.how_necessities_are_paid %></p>

<h2>Physical Address</h2>
<p>Street: <%= @energy_application.address %></p>
<p>Street Line 2: <%= @energy_application.address2 %></p>
<p>City: <%= @energy_application.city %></p>
<p>County: <%= @energy_application.county %></p>
<p>Zip: <%= @energy_application.zip %></p>

<h2>Mailing Address</h2>
<p>Street: <%= @energy_application.mailing_address_street %></p>
<p>City: <%= @energy_application.mailing_address_city %></p>
<p>County: <%= @energy_application.mailing_address_county %></p>
<p>State: <%= @energy_application.mailing_address_state %></p>
<p>Zip: <%= @energy_application.mailing_address_zip %></p>

<h2>Household Information</h2>
<p>Household Type: <%= @energy_application.household_type %></p>

<h2>Dwelling</h2>
<p>Type of Dwelling: <%= @energy_application.type_of_dwelling %></p>
<p>Residence Status: <%= @energy_application.residence_status %></p>
<p>Types of Heat: <%= @energy_application.types_of_heat %></p>
<p>Primary Heat Source: <%= @energy_application.primary_heat_source %></p>
<p>Secondary Heat Source: <%= @energy_application.secondary_heat_source %></p>
<p>Utility Company Benefit Goes To: <%= @energy_application.utility_company %></p>

<h2>Utility</h2>

<h2>COVID-19 Impact</h2>
<p>Household Impacted By COVID-19: <%= @energy_application.household_impacted_by_covid %></p>
<p>Loss of Employment: <%= @energy_application.covid_loss_of_employment %></p>
<p>Vulnerable Population: <%= @energy_application.covid_vulnerable_population %></p>
<p>Reduction of Hours/Unpaid Leave: <%= @energy_application.covid_reduction_of_hours %></p>
<p>Loss of Childcare/Children Home From School: <%= @energy_application.covid_loss_of_childcare %></p>
<p>Other Situation: <%= @energy_application.covid_other_situation %></p>
<p>COVID-19 Related Expenses: <%= @energy_application.covid_expenses %></p>

<div class="btn-group">
  <%= link_to "Back", energy_applications_path, class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
  <% if @energy_application.submission_date == nil %>
    <%= link_to "Edit", edit_energy_application_path(@energy_application), class: "btn btn-primary" %>
    <%= link_to "Delete", @energy_application, class: "btn btn-danger", method: :delete,
      data: { confirm: "Are you sure you want to delete this enitre application?" } %>
  <% end %>
</div>

<% if @energy_application.submission_date != nil %>
  <p><div class="alert alert-warning">Submitted applications can not be modified.</div></p>
<% end %>
